            <div class="img-wrapper mt-5 text-center">
                <div class="col content two-columns text-left">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Swap rates are applied only when there are positions kept open overnight.</li>
                        <li>Swap rates are applied at the end of the trading day or at 00:00 platform time.</li>
                        <li>Swap rates are calculated in points and can be positive or negative depending on the interest rate of the two currencies.</li>
                        <li>Swap rates are calculated and applied on every trading night, however on Wednesday night swap rates are charged at triple the usual rate to account for the weekend.</li>
                        <li>Each currency pair has its own swap charge and is measured on a standard size of 1 standard lot (100,000 base units).</li>
                    </ul>
